'''Hanava fruit''' was a fruit of a [[Hanava/Legends|hanava]] [[Tree/Legends|tree]] sometimes smuggled in order to avoid customs fees. The drawback of this was that some havana fruit cargos were infested with [[Greddleback termite/Legends|greddleback termites]], notably one that was transported to [[Bethal]].

